definitions.definition: Relating to or having the abilities of a psychic.
examples: You must be psychic —I was just about to say that.
She is a psychic person—she hears messages from beyond.

definitions.definition: Relating to the psyche or mind, or to mental activity in general.

main_definition: Relating to or having the abilities of a psychic.
secondary_definitions: Relating to the psyche or mind, or to mental activity in general.
